tool/vscode/case/m1.html.body:
大小写快捷键

路径：File -> Perferences -> Settings -> Keyboard Shortcuts

操作：

删除已有的快捷键 ctrl+shift+u 和 ctrl+u
点击右上角按钮，进入json格式，复制下面的内容，即可

// Place your key bindings in this file to overwrite the defaults
[
    {
        "key": "ctrl+shift+u",
        "command": "editor.action.transformToUppercase"
    },
    {
        "key": "ctrl+u",
        "command": "editor.action.transformToLowercase"
    }
]
